SUMMARY:Taco Tuesday Bike Ride
DESCRIPTION:A fun community bike ride through the heart of Santa Rosa. \nCome join us this Tuesday!\nWe roll through the JC and McDonald Ave neighborhood\, stop in Courthouse Square\, then on to the taco trucks at Mitote Food Park in Roseland for dinner!\nWe depart Mitote at 8:15pm\, ride back through Courthouse Square\, then on to Yogurt Farms for dessert.\nThis ride is 8 miles round trip and rides all year long.\nRides canceled for rain and holidays.\nAll riders welcome. Bring the whole family!\nMeet at SRJC parking lot at 550 Silva Ave. We are renting the use of this parking lot every Tuesday from 5:30pm to 9:30 pm. Taco Tuesday riders can park in the lot during that time frame for free.\nPlease park cars along the back wall on the east side. And stage in the row on the northern side of the lot (closest to Silva Ave). \nMeet at 5:30pm; pedals up at 6pm.\n 
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/taco-tuesday-bike-ride-20/
LOCATION:SRJC parking lot\, 550 Silva Ave\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Recreation
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Taco-Tuesday-bike-ride-3s-RowzQj.jpg
GEO:38.45872;-122.71660
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=SRJC parking lot 550 Silva Ave Santa Rosa CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=550 Silva Ave:geo:-122.71660,38.45872
END:VEVENT
