SUMMARY:Wednesday Night Comedy Open Mic
DESCRIPTION:Wednesday Night Comedy Open Mic-Downtown Santa Rosa. No cover\, free popcorn\, Bay Area comics\, & a fun crowd whether you go up or just watch.\nWednesday nights are for working it out\, trying new jokes\, and laughing with the local comedy community at Wednesday Night Comedy Open Mic at Barrel Proof Lounge in Downtown Santa Rosa .\nThis is a lively\, welcoming open mic that draws comedians from all over the Bay Area and beyond. Whether you’re getting on stage or just grabbing a drink and enjoying the show\, it’s always a fun\, unpredictable night.\nNo cover (2-drink minimum)\n🍿 Free popcorn\n🔞 21+\nComedian Info:\n• Pre-signups open at 10am via the BACN Facebook group\n• Limited 6:00pm in-person signups\n• 6:30pm bucket draw for set order\n• 3–4 minute sets (light at 1 minute remaining)\n• Hosted by Jon Lehre\nIt’s a great room for comics — and a great show even if you never touch the mic.\nCheck out www.barrelprooflounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/wednesday-night-comedy-open-mic-2/
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge\, 501 Mendocino Avenue\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Comedy
GEO:38.44260;-122.71573
