DESCRIPTION:Join us every Wednesday for Karaoke Night at Clubhouse Bar & Grill! Show kicks off at 8pm and we rock out until close! \nWar Pigs BBQ has AMAZING coming from the kitchen and GREAT drinks are served at the bar. \nMake some lifelong memories with some of the best people you will ever meet! \n*No cover*
