SUMMARY:Big Stage Karaoke Wednesdays with KJ Danny D
DESCRIPTION:Wednesday nights at Barrel Proof Lounge just got louder\, sexier\, and way more fun.\nKaraoke moves to the main showroom big stage every Wednesday at 9pm\, following Open Mic\, and runs until late. Hosting the night is KJ Danny D (Danny Duclos)—one of the most popular and in-demand karaoke hosts around. We’re genuinely stoked to have him bringing his style\, energy\, and crowd-moving presence to Downtown Santa Rosa.\nThis isn’t sleepy bar karaoke. Danny brings a fresh\, high-energy approach that turns singing into a full-on late-night experience. Big stage\, great sound\, packed room\, and the kind of momentum that keeps people singing well past closing time.\n🎤 Main showroom\n🕘 Starts 9pm (after Open Mic)\n🎟 No cover\n📍 Downtown Santa Rosa\nCheck out www.barrelprooflounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/big-stage-karaoke-wednesdays-with-kj-danny-d-7/
